&CP2K
 PROGRAM      Quickstep
 PROJECT      H2O
 IOLEVEL      10
 FFTLIB       FFTSG
&END

&DFT
 FUNCTIONAL   Pade
 LSD
&END

&QS
 CUTOFF       150
&END

&SCF
 GUESS        ATOMIC
 MAX_SCF      2
&END

&PRINT MEDIUM
&END

&KIND C
 BASIS_SET    DZVP-GTH-PADE
 POTENTIAL    GTH-PADE-q4
&END
&KIND N
 BASIS_SET    DZVP-GTH-PADE
 POTENTIAL    GTH-PADE-q5
&END

&CELL
 UNIT         ANGSTROM
 ABC          8.0  5.0  5.0
&END

&COORD
 N 0.0 0.0 0.0
 C 2.0 0.0 0.0
&END
